'''擁抱機'''（{{lang-en|Hug machine}}），又稱擁抱箱等，是一種深部壓覺裝置，能夠安撫[[过度敏感|过度敏感]]的人，比如[[自閉症譜系障礙|自閉症譜系障礙]]患者。這種裝置是由[[天寶·葛蘭汀|天寶·葛蘭汀]]在上大學時發明的。<ref>{{cite book |last=Grandin |first=Temple |title=Thinking in Pictures: And Other Reports from My Life with Autism |isbn=9780385477925 |location=New York |publisher=Doubleday |year=1995 |url=https://archive.org/details/thinkinginpictur00gran }}</ref><ref name="Emergence">{{cite book |last1=Grandin |first1=Temple |last2=Scariano |first2=Margaret M. |title=Emergence: Labeled Autistic |page=[https://archive.org/details/emergencelabeled00gran/page/91 91] |publisher=Grand Central Publishing |year=1996 |isbn=9780446671828 |url=https://archive.org/details/emergencelabeled00gran/page/91 }}</ref>

因為[[自閉症|自閉症]]會影響人的社交和敏感度，葛蘭汀針對這一問題，設計了用於緩解感官的擁抱機。

== 功能 ==
它在某些感官過度敏感的患者身上（通常即自閉患者），有舒緩壓力的功效，她自己也曾是這機器的長期使用者。而隨後學者的研究<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.autism-help.org/points-grandin-hug-machine.htm | title = Temple Grandin's Hug Machine | author = Stephen M. Edelson, Ph.D. | publisher = Center for the Study of Autism | location = Salem, Oregon | date = 6 December 2009 | accessdate = 2011-11-09 | archive-date = 2020-11-11 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201111210440/http://www.autism-help.org/points-grandin-hug-machine.htm | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref> {{cite journal |author=Edelson, S.M., Edelson MG, Kerr DC, Grandin T |title=Behavioral and physiological effects of deep pressure on children with autism: a pilot study evaluating the efficacy of Grandin's Hug Machine |journal=Am J Occup Ther |volume=53 |issue=2 |pages=145–52 |year=1999 |pmid=10200837}} </ref>，也多支持其減輕壓力的效果，但卻不完全同意消除焦躁的功能。<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=fn_9f5x0f1Q |title=Temple Grandin: The world needs all kinds of minds  |access-date=2020-09-11 |archive-date=2021-02-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210216155303/https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=fn_9f5x0f1Q |dead-url=no }}</ref>

